Sophus (version dvo_slam compliant). Courtesy of H.Strasdat

C++ implementation of Lie Groups using Eigen.

## Note
This Package is not up-to-date with Sophus by H.Strasdat.
But it allows the dvo_slam suite compilation


Thanks to Steven Lovegrove, Sophus is now fully templated  - using the Curiously Recurring Template Pattern (CRTP).

(In order to go back to the non-templated/double-only version "git checkout a621ff".)

Installation guide:

>>>
cd Sophus
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
<<<


